        <Parent_String>Srivijaya (Javanese) [300018761], Central Javanese [300018723], Javanese (culture or style) [300018721], Indonesian regional styles and periods [300018710], Indonesian (culture or style) [300018704], Southeast Asian [300120146], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
